sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Client as 📱 Utilisateur / Client
    participant API as 🚀 Next.js API (/api/search/visual)
    participant HF as 🤗 Hugging Face Space (fabiol237-vestyle-ai-engine)
    participant Supabase as 🗄️ Supabase DB (pgvector)
    participant Mistral as 🤖 Pixtral Vision (Fallback)
    participant Voyage as 🧠 Voyage AI (Fallback)

    Client->>API: POST /api/search/visual (Image, category_filter)
    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        note right of API: MOTEUR PRINCIPAL (Hugging Face)
        API->>HF: Call "search" endpoint (Base64 Image)
        activate HF
        HF->>HF: Run Florence-2 (Caption & OCR)
        HF->>HF: Run DINOv2 (Structural features)
        HF->>HF: Run SigLIP (Semantic features)
        HF->>HF: Fusion vector (1024 dims)
        HF->>Supabase: Query similarity (pgvector HNSW)
        Supabase-->>HF: Return Top Matched Products
        HF-->>API: Return products, description, OCR tags
        deactivate HF
    end

    alt Si HF Space échoue / Timeout
        rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
            note right of API: MOTEUR FALLBACK
            API->>Mistral: POST Chat completion (Image + VISION_PROMPT)
            Mistral-->>API: Return Image Description
            API->>Voyage: POST Multimodal embedding (Image + Description)
            Voyage-->>API: Return Embedding (1024D)
            API->>Supabase: Call RPC match_products_v2(embedding)
            Supabase-->>API: Return Top Matched Products
        end
    end

    API->>API: Post-process (filter by category, limit to 12)
    API-->>Client: Response (success, products, engine, elapsed_ms)